    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare the effectiveness of the community mobile outreach approach in improving treatment
      outcomes (success rate) among tuberculosis patients with those being treated with facility
      based directly observed treatment short course (DOTS) in Jeddah region.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
